Content.details:
Turning on IBC transfers for the native token NAM. This allows NAM to be transferred out of Namada over IBC and back into Namada the same way. The per-epoch throughput limit is set to 20M NAM.

The code used to generate the WASM attached to this proposal can be found here: https://github.com/anoma/namada-governance-upgrades/blob/ea7e6f6d413a4f8399cb995e782b4aadbe6dda4f/phase5b/src/lib.rs.

Please see the forum discussion linked here for more details.
Content.title: Phase 5 IBC transfers for NAM
